Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:02.47,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眩しい風のなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描くよ　君の笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:11.35,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直になれる瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:14.77,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小さなことで揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:18.37,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}弱い自分が悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:22.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泣きたいときだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:24.28,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}上を向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:29.96,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わたしだけにできることがあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.08,0:01:38.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あきらめないよ　君を守り続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:44.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とまらないスピードで想いがあふれていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:50.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰よりも輝いていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:53.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星がみえない日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光はある　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:59.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じること…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:03.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い、　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:10.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの空で逢えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================opcn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:02.47,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}炫目的風中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描繪你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:11.35,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}變得坦率的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:14.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因小事而動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:18.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}軟弱的自己令我懊惱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:22.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:24.28,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也仰頭忍淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:29.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}必定有唯有我能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.08,0:01:38.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永不言棄 一直守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:44.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思念正以停不下的速度膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不想認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:50.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願比任何人都耀目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:53.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使夜空沒有繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}亦會有光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:59.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:03.01,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}前往未來的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:10.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能在那片天空相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================zhengwen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這來電鈴聲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你好～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi～ 我是大家的偶像 篠之之束哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等 別掛啊 小箒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 吾妹喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 姐姐知道你有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要是吧～只屬於你的專用機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然已經準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高性能兼規格爆表
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,325)\fs16}（High End）     （Over Spec）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟「小白」平起平坐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台機體的名字叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「紅椿」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,900)\bord2\blur4\pos(470,120)\fs26\1c&HE4E4E4&\3c&H2D2D2D&}到了海邊已經十一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,900)\bord2\blur4\pos(470,93)\fs16\1c&HE4E4E4&\3c&H2D2D2D&}Oceans Eleven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 已經到早上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 快遮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說夫婦之間不應有所隱瞞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且你還是我老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間你到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本 對自己中意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都是叫「我老婆」之類的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰向你灌輸這種錯誤的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要多訓練一下寢技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想磨練寢技的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以陪你練哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉紅什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始晨練了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為是星期天就鬆懈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然擅闖別人夫婦的寢室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫婦?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 箒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天誅!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 一大早就害慘我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只叫了我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就要到海邊實習了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你不是說沒有女裝泳衣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛好也想買條泳褲 就順便咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 就知道是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 你說什麼了 夏爾魯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏洛特!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你答應過獨處的時候這麼叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦對 抱歉啊 夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄少女純情的男人 被馬踹死就最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這種傢伙的確該死一死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你生什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽手的話 就原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟在陌生城市走散了很麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大木頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…是不是在牽手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 原來我沒看錯也沒發白日夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然牽手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 宰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 挺開心的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉烏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我沒有傷害你們的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是加入他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟未知的敵人戰鬥 首先要收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先跟蹤 查清楚他們的關係到底到什麼地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:05:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道你是女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫夏洛特就太一般了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要麼想個別的稱呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只限於你我之間的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…叫夏露怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既順口又親暱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露…嗯 好 相當好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然這麼大反應 看來她相當喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露…夏露嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「有點特別的存在」的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還得買點其他東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買其他東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿好啊 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄掉的話 有你好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你買的也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初三的夏天是很特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳池用泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙灘用泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決勝泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級決勝泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級無敵級決勝泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須做好多手準備 以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 你也來買東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們買好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是游泳用的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這傢伙憋足了勁要曬給你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自言自語罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:07:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏哥也來買泳裝麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 馬上要到海邊實習了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就叫一夏哥幫挑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 明年我就要當一夏的學妹了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要考IS學園啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是第一志願
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那你要加油備考哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 哥他去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 跟我來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿這老哥沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 一夏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼硬拉我進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 只是想你看看我挑的泳衣合不合適
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不用一起進試衣室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道察覺到我們在跟蹤了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年推薦可以推擠起胸部的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全都是泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上原來有各種各樣的泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得好好挑一挑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿了不合適的泳衣 男朋友會討厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算其他事全拿滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣穿挫了就致命了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她們找到肯定會礙事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外頭有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你就留在這 我馬上換好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然趁勢做了這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 夏露想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂 完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豁出去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她 她真的脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能想像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想其他事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 圓周率是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,π=3.1415926535897932384626433832
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換好了…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不會啊 相當給力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要這套了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音 該不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織織織斑 迪諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 就算是同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必須劃清界線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤男寡女進試衣室是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然海邊實習將近 可以理解兩位的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到老師也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貿然出去就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是繼續觀望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉麗莎 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉烏拉·博迪薇希隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是關於那個織斑一夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 織斑教官的弟弟 還是隊長中意的男士麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是你教我的 也就是…我老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要到海邊實習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不知道挑選泳衣的基準是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問問你的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 我們黑兔部隊 常與隊長同在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問一下 目前隊長所有的裝備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有學校指定的泳衣一件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得IS學園是用舊式校園泳衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件也挺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 穿那件的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿那件的話?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一件普通的深色泳衣罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是黑兔部隊的副隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本動漫的狂熱愛好者可不是蓋的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 山人自有妙計
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是十一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚之前都是自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得準時回旅館 別過了吃晚飯時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 阿織 跟我們一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩沙灘排球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好啊 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好高好高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠方都看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊 你是貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好像很好玩 我也要試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她完了到我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是展望台 快下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了還不明白麼 移動監視塔遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 你忘了在巴士上答應過我什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來～一夏 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓一夏幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見 幫忙塗太陽油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違背和淑女之間的約定 可不是紳士的所為哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 把手弄暖了再幫我塗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我還是第一次做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼開心幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好像好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都心跳加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉亞 等下也借我太陽油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 只塗背後就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不機會難得 麻煩塗滿我手夠不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塗滿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳 還有…屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我幫你塗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一寸～肌膚～都塗滿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡你也想塗是吧 塗啊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴 別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為啥是我挨打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 我們鬥快游到那邊的浮標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了要請吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別自顧自決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 太卑鄙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然挺對不起塞西莉亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次機會就讓給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能輸給塞西莉亞和拉烏拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…一夏的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鈴 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你回旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我要跟一夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹月 能幫一下我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 我幫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖聽話去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼精神 應該沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 原來你在這
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這浴巾妖怪是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 給一夏看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有問題我說了算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音 是拉烏拉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得換了身泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得讓一夏看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等 我也得做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就跟一夏到海裡玩咯 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想笑就儘管笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪吧 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我…可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是第一次聽人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說好的 打沙灘排球咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 跟阿織對打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好三對三
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪諾亞也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們見識一下我七月夏日惡魔的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好接球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛 他說我可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉烏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉烏拉 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他 他 他說我可愛 我我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉烏拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別管她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙灘排球啊 好像很好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:19:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 你看怎樣 織斑老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑老師 好像模特兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 老師 我跟你換
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏你…是不是喜歡織斑老師那種類型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為反應差太多了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到我們的泳衣都不是這反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手真多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到織斑老師還算一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 千冬姐是強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏…估計你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好要發球了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 千冬…織斑老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你有點心神不定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在擔心什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天我聯繫了她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉烏拉的VT系統 似乎跟她無關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是7月7日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 說不定會現身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然已經準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高性能兼規格爆表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟「小白」平起平坐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台機體的名字叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「紅椿」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂喂 那人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄逸的裙子+兔耳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超有視覺衝擊力的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了這裡 IS的關鍵人物終於登場?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.92,0:23:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎給篠之之帶禮物來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲 沒時間吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還飛來了意想不到的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 站立於境界線上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(354,325)\fs16}（Thin·Red·Line）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.42,0:24:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快樂的海邊實習
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急轉直下 要出大事了
